headline: Why the Best Time to Own Generac Stock Is Now
summary: Generac  stock has been frustrating and difficult for investors to time.  For years, shares have been whipsawed by storms, data-center developments, and problems with its own inventory.  The stock appears to be ready to buy, finally.
